text: Kyabé () is a city in the Moyen-Chari Region, Chad. It is the administrative center of the Lac Iro Department. There is an airport with the name of the city, Kyabé Airport. ==Population== Population by years: {| class="wikitable" border="1" |+ ! 1993 !! 2009 |- | 11,912 || 15,960 |} ==References== Category:Populated places in Chad
